# React Score Calculator App

## Description

This project demonstrates React Function Components, Props, and CSS Styling. It calculates and displays a student's score based on the total marks and goal.

## Technologies Used

- React
- JavaScript (ES6)
- HTML
- CSS
- Node.js
- npm

## Features

- Function Component
- Props
- CSS Styling
- Score Calculation
- Component Rendering

## Project Structure

```
scorecalculatorapp
│
├── src
│   ├── Components
│   │   └── CalculateScore.js
│   ├── Stylesheets
│   │   └── mystyle.css
│   ├── App.js
│   └── index.js
```

## Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/scorecalculatorapp.git
cd scorecalculatorapp
npm install
npm start
```

